{"tid":2131413,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾南山倡香港全民核酸篩查　指非常時期堅決打擊搞集會人士","createTime":"2020-07-30T00:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T03:21:19.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d9fab04ccd3a3b5cb6c4582d75aefed2c44df6f6","tid":2131413,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T00:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image2.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/hd/b0f5e5e72bcda7abb7c19f5aa4e39c17/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200730/_2020073007443671478.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2Fb0f5e5e72bcda7abb7c19f5aa4e39c17%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200730%2F_2020073007443671478.jpg&h=f7ce2fcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鍾南山倡香港全民核酸篩查。<br />\n<br />\n本港新冠肺炎持續爆發，國家衛健委高級別專家組組長鍾南山表示，在香港已出現社區傳染，但確診數字未有幾何級數增長，說明政府及社會干預起了很大作用，目前疫情處於拉鋸戰關鍵期，建議香港要進一步強化和落實目前的防控措施，同時開展全民核酸篩查，要行政上要求檢測，另外要增加檢測材料、人員、強化簡易醫院建設等。<br />\n<br />\n鍾南山接受央視訪問時指，香港應從檢測試劑及人力方面提供支持，主要不是醫療問題，而是公共衛生防控問題，亦要加強香港與內地在防控和醫療救治方面的交流。他續指，在防控非常時期，要堅決打擊搞聚集集會的人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1832596/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%8D%BE%E5%8D%97%E5%B1%B1%E5%80%A1%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E6%A0%B8%E9%85%B8%E7%AF%A9%E6%9F%A5-%E6%8C%87%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E6%99%82%E6%9C%9F%E5%A0%85%E6%B1%BA%E6%89%93%E6%93%8A%E6%90%9E%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1832596%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E9%258D%25BE%25E5%258D%2597%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E5%2580%25A1%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E9%2585%25B8%25E7%25AF%25A9%25E6%259F%25A5-%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%259C%259F%25E5%25A0%2585%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%2590%259E%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGO